      <title>波兰极右翼总统候选人以堕胎立场打击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/polish-far-right-presidential-candidate-hit-for-abortion-stance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波兰总统候选人斯拉沃米尔·曼茨森（Slawomir Mentzen）表示，当该国于五月份前往大选时，他反对反对强奸受害者的堕胎，引起了反对者的愤怒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/polish-far-right-presidential-candidate-hit-for-abortion-stance</guid>
