    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，他与律师事务所Skadden达到了1亿美元的无偿交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-says-he-s-reached-100-million-pro-bono-deal-with-skadden</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统宣布，他已经与律师事务所Skadden，Arps，Slate，Meagher＆amp;达成了协议。 Flom为其政府的优先事项提供至少1亿美元的Bono法律工作，这是一家白鞋公司提供服务的最新实例，以避免联邦政府可能制裁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-says-he-s-reached-100-million-pro-bono-deal-with-skadden</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 17:12:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Zelenskiy看到更多的欧洲战争援助，因为美国浮动新交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/ukraine-to-get-more-intelligence-from-europeans-zelenskiy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy）表示，由于与美国的紧张关系，欧洲盟友将分享额外的军事情报，并加强联合防空和炮兵生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/ukraine-to-get-more-intelligence-from-europeans-zelenskiy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 16:39:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>经济学家将加拿大的增长预测作为贸易战争的罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/economists-slash-canada-growth-forecasts-as-trade-war-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着与美国的贸易战争，加拿大的增长趋势和较高的通货膨胀率在一项新调查中预测，经济学家预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/economists-slash-canada-growth-forecasts-as-trade-war-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 16:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>万斯（Vance）作为美国枪支来控制格陵兰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/vance-arrives-in-greenland-with-us-gunning-for-control-of-island</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统杰德·万斯（JD Vance）说，丹麦在周五下午参观格陵兰的一家军事设施时，丹麦“在确保格陵兰岛安全方面做得并没有做得很好”，因为唐纳德·特朗普总统重申了他对美国对偏远和资源丰富的北极岛的渴望作为美国领土。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/vance-arrives-in-greenland-with-us-gunning-for-control-of-island</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 16:15:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普，卡尼谈论新政，加拿大当选后的计划会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-carney-talk-amid-trade-spat-plan-to-meet-after-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统说，他与加拿大总理马克·卡尼（Mark Carney）进行了交谈，两人将在加拿大当选后开会，这在附近的盟友和主要贸易伙伴之间发动了加剧的关税战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-carney-talk-amid-trade-spat-plan-to-meet-after-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:14:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当特朗普煽动共和党攻击时，美国企业美国抛弃了绿色债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/corporate-america-ditches-green-bonds-as-trump-emboldens-gop-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）返回白宫以来，美国公司几乎放弃了曾经被吹捧为美国企业美国掌握地球的绿色债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/corporate-america-ditches-green-bonds-as-trump-emboldens-gop-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 15:03:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼古拉创始人特雷弗·米尔顿（Trevor Milton）在欺诈定罪后被特朗普赦免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nikola-founder-milton-pardoned-by-trump-after-fraud-conviction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼古拉公司（Nikola Corp.）创始人特雷弗·米尔顿（Trevor Milton）因唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统赦免了对电费制造商的财务进步而被定罪的欺诈罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/nikola-founder-milton-pardoned-by-trump-after-fraud-conviction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 14:47:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>两家大型律师事务所起诉特朗普作为第三次定居，以避免秩序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-targeted-firms-hit-back-with-suits-challenging-orders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[律师事务所Jenner＆amp;布洛克（Block）和威尔默海尔（Wilmerhale）提起诉讼，要求挑战唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对他们的命令，而同行斯卡达登（Skadden）避免了政府行动，并承诺将做1亿美元的无偿工作。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-targeted-firms-hit-back-with-suits-challenging-orders</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 13:59:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队的信号聊天是美国间谍的暴露方法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-s-team-signal-chat-exposed-us-spycraft-to-adversaries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统在信号聊天中驳回了披露胡塞（Houthi）攻击计划的“小故障”，对国家安全没有影响。情报专家认为，它使外国对手对美国间谍的无价洞察力远远超出了明显的范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-28/trump-s-team-signal-chat-exposed-us-spycraft-to-adversaries</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Mar 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
